{"tid":2442474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"欠債2,500億 包商銀行破產","createTime":"2021-03-11T11:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T14:07:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"79de07d3abd2f504ed37ba402e94f6b88223d786","tid":2442474,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:21:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210311/72SVZYFGENBD5PSXHL5YBFFIGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210311%2F72SVZYFGENBD5PSXHL5YBFFIGI%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=cc19d553\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210311%2F72SVZYFGENBD5PSXHL5YBFFIGI%2F&h=31f90bde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210311/72SVZYFGENBD5PSXHL5YBFFIGI/</a><br />\n<br />\n欠債2,500億 包商銀行破產<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/P_h-JAH6-LdbmccywIeGXlXV8L4=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/256JMQELUZF2BB7JMTUWO4MK2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FP_h-JAH6-LdbmccywIeGXlXV8L4%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F256JMQELUZF2BB7JMTUWO4MK2A.jpg&h=ee1d6084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■與「明天系」關係密切的包商銀行正式破產。路透社<br />\n<br />\n與被喻為中共權貴「白手套」、內地財金「明天系」創辦人肖建華關係密切的中國包商銀行，自2019年5月因出現嚴重信用風險而被官方接管後，近日再證實已於上月7日被北京法院裁定破產。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肖建華「明天系」擁九成股份<br />\n<br />\n據內媒近日引述法院發佈的裁定書顯示，包商銀行於去年11月申請破產清算時，已無任何生產經營、在職人員，其負債總額為逾2,059億元人民幣（下同．約2,490億港元），明顯已「資不抵債」，沒實際清償能力。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述資料指，包商銀行的興衰與目前遭當局監管的「明天系」（明天控股集團）關係密切，當中「明天系」對包商銀行的持股「一股獨大」，比例高達89.27%。「明天系」在2005年至2019年間，透過註冊逾200間空殼公司，以借款方式取得信貸資金，涉資高達1,560億元（約1,887億港元），其後該筆款項形成不良貸款。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有多名全國人大代表在。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「明天系」創辦人肖建華2017年1月在香港四季酒店失蹤後，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n21世紀經濟報道"},{"pid":"c8418726d4b4e4e90fa8fbab07ccef545c61c714","tid":2442474,"uid":4826,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:34:58.000Z","msg":"「明天系」創辦人肖建華2017年1月在香港四季酒店失蹤後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪搭直升機閃左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95833d6a290919115d879eacd2ab69e410272a2","tid":2442474,"uid":44458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:36:13.000Z","msg":"最緊要有連鎖反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37035bb27e02a34e22885f1c5b789acd48a39abe","tid":2442474,"uid":342828,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:41:15.000Z","msg":"唔驚，有翠翠財務提供欠債一筆清。"},{"pid":"826abc945c8856826d1cffd7fe5adebb0c7ac08e","tid":2442474,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:41:25.000Z","msg":"200間空殻都借到錢呀？ 唔駛審查架？"},{"pid":"d30bda4781c535e1b4abcaedcda5863d2432630d","tid":2442474,"uid":241628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:44:53.000Z","msg":"信政府&nbsp;唔怕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4579de73f18b4df3d0e30caeeadb5010fb5d5c88","tid":2442474,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:45:35.000Z","msg":"火燒連環船<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29813d8a64adab84f393362726ecda2a41b84e8c","tid":2442474,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b95833d6a290919115d879eacd2ab69e410272a2","tid":2442474,"uid":44458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:36:13.000Z","msg":"最緊要有連鎖反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm